/-- The `simp_ifs_simps` simp attribute. -/
initialize simpIfsSimpExt : SimpExtension ←
  registerSimpAttr `simp_ifs_simps "\
    The `simp_ifs_simps` attribute registers simp lemmas to be used by `simp_ifs`."

